        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Covers most tall users up to about 6'3"–6'4". No taller cylinder option exists — 20.5" is a hard limit. Users above 6'4" who need more seat height should consider the Steelcase Gesture (21") or Leap Plus (22.5").</p>
